                        <div id="q10" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqPunchExter">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Hyundai vehicles typically have slightly better resale value than Tata, though both are decent in this segment.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p></p>
                <p><span class="font-weight-700">BikeCarHub</span> always recommends taking a test drive of both vehicles to feel the difference yourself before making a purchase.</p>
